		"name": "logic_ConvoComplete",
		"value": 0,
		"min": 0,
		"max": 1,
		"text": "The update node uses this variable to gauge whether the convo is complete, so it knows if it should jump to the dashboard.\n\nMake sure this gets set to 1 wherever the convo ends.",
